&lt;td width=&quot;40%&quot;&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Duty 1&lt;/strong&gt; exercise leadership in the church through helping it to discern appropriate vision and strategy and to shape its culture&lt;/p&gt;
