&lt;p&gt;S2, S5, S6, S7, S9, S10&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;B1, B2, B3, B4, B5, B6, B7&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/td&gt;
&lt;/tr&gt;
&lt;tr&gt;
&lt;td width=&quot;40%&quot;&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Duty 5&lt;/strong&gt; supervise, manage and support both volunteers and paid staff&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/td&gt;
&lt;td width=&quot;20%&quot;&gt;
&lt;p&gt;K1, K2, K4&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;S1, S4, S5, S8&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;B1, B2, B3, B4, B5, B6, B7&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/td&gt;
&lt;/tr&gt;
&lt;tr&gt;
&lt;td width=&quot;40%&quot;&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Duty 6&lt;/strong&gt; participate in meetings within the church and in the community, often chairing or taking a leading role in those meetings - these meetings may relate to any other aspect of the role&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/td&gt;
&lt;td width=&quot;20%&quot;&gt;
&lt;p&gt;K1, K2, K4&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;S1, S2, S3, S4, S5, S6, S8, S9&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;B1, B2, B3, B4, B5, B6, B7&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/td&gt;
&lt;/tr&gt;
&lt;tr&gt;
&lt;td width=&quot;40%&quot;&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Duty 7&lt;/strong&gt; offer pastoral care within both the church and the local community, for example to those seeking guidance in making life choices or looking for support in times of illness or bereavement or stressful circumstances&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/td&gt;
&lt;td width=&quot;20%&quot;&gt;
&lt;p&gt;K8, K4, K9, K10&lt;/p&gt;
