&lt;p&gt;B1, B2, B3, B4, B5, B6, B7&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/td&gt;
&lt;/tr&gt;
&lt;tr&gt;
&lt;td width=&quot;40%&quot;&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Duty 8&lt;/strong&gt; enable anyone interested in exploring or developing faith to do so, whether or not they are currently members of the church, through offering individual counsel and activities for groups of various sizes, and making use of a range of means to communicate&lt;/p&gt;
