&lt;p&gt;B1, B2, B3, B4, B5, B6, B7&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/td&gt;
&lt;/tr&gt;
&lt;tr&gt;
&lt;td width=&quot;40%&quot;&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Duty 9&lt;/strong&gt; represent their church in interaction with the wider community, including acting to promote the wellbeing of the locality and beyond&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/td&gt;
