&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Duty 11&#160;&lt;/strong&gt;Maintain their own personal and professional development through ongoing training, study and reflective practice. In order to continually enhance their understanding and practice of faith and ministry.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/td&gt;
&lt;td width=&quot;20%&quot;&gt;
&lt;p&gt;K5, K6, K7&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;S13, S17, S19, S20&lt;/p&gt;
